extendedInfo.description: Contains all of the words from our PSAT, SAT and GRE apps in one convenient app!-Based on Android Developer Challenge top 10 finalist Flash of Genius: SAT Vocab-Written by SAT and GRE tutors from Harvard and MIT-Includes high quality audio pronunciations-Includes over 750 words!-Adapts to your learning styleGet it!
